    "created_at": "2012-07-06T12:10:58Z",
    "updated_at": "2012-07-06T12:10:58Z",
    "body": "Perhaps we could implement `arc::exclusive` in a way that does not trivially deadlock?  I believe the problem is that it uses pthread mutexes and are scheduler in unaware of those.  It seems like we should implement mutexes in our scheduler if we need them in our implementation.\n",
