    "created_at": "2012-07-11T19:26:32Z",
    "updated_at": "2012-07-11T19:26:32Z",
    "body": "Exclusives will always be unsafe because putting exclusives inside of exclusives can result in exchange heap leaks. Yet exclusives-in-exclusives might be desirable in some cases, so even if we could use the type system to prevent it (which seems infeasible), we shouldn't.\n\nConclusion: They stay unsafe.\n",
